---
layout: base.njk
title: FinalShell 官方下载
---

<style>
    /* 强制重置父级容器，防止 11ty 自动生成的容器干扰 */
    body, html {
        background-color: #0f172a !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
        color: #f1f5f9;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* 顶部导航锁定 */
    .site-header {
        background: #1e293b;
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* 主容器限制 */
    .main-container {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* 核心修复：英雄区域图片锁死 */
    .hero-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 60px 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
    }

    /* 强制限制图片大小，解决“越来越大”的问题 */
    .img-box {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px; /* 这里锁死 800px */
        margin: 30px auto;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .img-box img {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: auto !important;
        display: block !important;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    /* 按钮样式 */
    .download-btn {
        background: #38bdf8;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 15px 40px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    /* 文章列表区域 */
    .layout-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 40px;
        margin-top: 50px;
    }
    
    .article-body {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 300px;
        background: #1e293b;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .sidebar {
        width: 300px;
    }

    .sidebar a {
        color: #38bdf8;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: block;
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
</style>

<header class="site-header">
    <div class="main-container">
        <strong style="font-size: 24px;">FinalShell SSH</strong>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="main-container">
        <h1>新一代 SSH 管理工具</h1>
        <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.2rem;">集成终端、文件传输与系统监控</p>
        
        <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="#" class="download-btn">Windows 版本下载</a>
        </div>

        <div class="img-box">
            <img src="https://pc1.gtimg.com/guanjia/images/2b/b1/2bb1dee1d6433f1ef0f3a185eeb0d908.jpg" alt="FinalShell Preview">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<main class="main-container">
    <div class="layout-grid">
        <article class="article-body">
            <h2>为什么选择 FinalShell？</h2>
            <p>FinalShell 完美融合了 SSH 终端和 SFTP 客户端，支持多平台，提供实时服务器性能监控曲线。</p>
            <div class="img-box" style="max-width: 100%;">
                <img src="https://pc1.gtimg.com/guanjia/images/2b/b1/2bb1dee1d6433f1ef0f3a185eeb0d908.jpg" alt="Features">
            </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="sidebar">
            <h3 style="color: #fff;">最新更新</h3>
            {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
                <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            {% else %}
                <p>暂无内容</p>
            {% endfor %}
        </aside>
    </div>
</main>

<footer style="text-align: center; padding: 60px 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px;">
    &copy; 2026 FinalShell SSH.
</footer>